HEADWORD: indexation
<hw>indexation</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a system of economic regulation
in which wages and interest are tied to the cost-of-living index in
order to compensate for the effects of inflation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

